<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
<tr>
	<td width="1%">&nbsp;</td>
	<td width="98%">
	<br>
		<table border="1" width="100%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="0" bordercolor="#808080">
		  <tr>
		<td width="100%" colspan="2" bgcolor="#808080" background="/images/tb_silver.gif">
		  <p align="center"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>
		  Coldain Smuggler</font></b><br><a href = "../Subscribe.asp?DID=337344" ><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></td>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="100%" colspan="2" align="middle">
		    
			<BR><FONT FACE="Verdana" size="3">0 Screenshots Available!</FONT><BR><BR>
			
			</td>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="100%" colspan="2">
		    &nbsp;
		</td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td valign="top" width="50%"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Beast Name:</font><br></b>
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2">Coldain Smuggler&nbsp;</font></td>
		    <td valign="top" width="50%"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>
		    Location:</font><br></b>
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2"><A href="../geography/default.asp?MAPID=293942">Great Divide</a>&nbsp;</font>
		    </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="50%" valign="top" rowspan="2" nowrap><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Known Level Range:</font><br></b>
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2">38 / 42&nbsp;</font></td>
		    <td width="50%" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>
		    Quest Related: </font></b>
				No
			 </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="50%" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Magic Caster: </font></b>
				No
		    </td>
		    </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="50%" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Faction Hits:</font></b><br>
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    Unknown
		    &nbsp;
		    </font>
		    </td>
		    <td width="50%" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Loot:</font></b>&nbsp;
		    
		    <br>
		    <font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    Unknown
		     &nbsp;
		    </font>
		    </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td align="middle" width="100%" valign="top" colspan="2"><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Description</font></b>
		    </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
		    <td width="100%" valign="top" colspan="2"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
			In searching for ways to ride the fence in factions and perhaps befriend both Giants, Dragon Claws and Midgets of this continent we decided to risk an onslaught against a Coldain Smuggler.  He was nestled in a cave near the Kodiak caves in the southwestern section of the Great Divide.  Mr. Smuggler did not respond to a hail, even though he was merely indifferent to a Barbarian Shaman. If I remember right, he became apprehensive when we returned grouped with a mischievous cleric, who conned him blue at level 43.<BR>
  Good thinking shorty, time to be apprehensive. We couldn't keep the pet healed. He boxed our tank into a greasy pool of fat. Double dotted him for approximately 400 total dmg. He was down 75% health when we knew we had to gate. It was a feeble attempt, but we were hoping by chance that he was weaker, and similar in faction to smugglers in HighPass or Iksar Pariahs in Kunark.<BR>
  Cave entrance should be Northeast East of the Labyrinth of Velketor entrance.  I might add, this cave is west and down the cliff from and empty and extensive cave. Perhaps the empty cave will be populated in future patches, but I even cast See Invisible on myself to assure, there was nothing there. Pulled to the empty caves for about 3 hours, nothing popped. Good place for a slumber party. If you kill the Coldain Smuggler, drop in and let us know what faction he gives.
		  
		  </font>
		  </td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr>
