				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Spawns in the right hand branch of the smaller Kodiak cave (the Kodiak cave directly downslope from Velkator's).  Had been pulling bears for several hours, when this little punk aggro'd me.<BR>
<BR>
We had a full group, and he con'd red to our 41 chanter (the highest level char in our group).  Was actually a little upset by this encounter.  I am a Zek worshiping Troll, so I began as &quot;apprehensive&quot; in Thurgadin - able to wander freely, make purchases, bank, etc.<BR>
<BR>
&quot;Coldain Smuggler&quot;  had different ideas.  When we killed him (the quickest most efficient way of removing aggro IMHTO &lt;in my humble troll opinion&gt;)<BR>
 we took seious faction hits against Coldain and Coldain King.  Also received positive giant factions but thats not the point.<BR>
<BR>
I've never encountered a mob before, that was part of a faction (and gave factions hits against) that i was not KOS to that would aggro me.  Was planning on hunting giants anyway, so this problem is easily fixed.  But, if you are in the caves be careful of your Dwarf Faction.<BR>
<BR>
By the way, I petitioned this.  When I told the GM I was aggro'd by a mob bearing a faction which I am not KOS to, he promptly said &quot;Doesn't sound like a bug to me.  I'll submit it to testing.  Have a nice night.&quot;  Uhh, yeah ok.  
				</font>
